diff-size-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-2414">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>xdiff_file_bdiff_size()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><p>     The following code applies reads a size of file that would be created     after applying a binary diff.    </p></div>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>$length </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">xdiff_string_bdiff_size</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'file.bdiff'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Resulting file will be </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$length</span><span style="color: #DD0000"> bytes long"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.xdiff-file-bdiff-size-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link xdiff_file_bdiff()} - Make binary diff of two files</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link xdiff_file_rabdiff()} - Make binary diff of two files using the Rabin's polynomial fingerprinting algorithm</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link xdiff_file_bpatch()} - Patch a file with a binary diff</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
