></span></strong> if an internal error happened.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.xdiff-string-diff-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-2424">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>xdiff_string_diff()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><p>     The following code makes unified diff of two articles.    </p></div>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>$old_article </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">file_get_contents</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'./old_article.txt'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$new_article </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$_REQUEST</span><span style="color: #007700">[</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'article'</span><span style="color: #007700">]; </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// Let's say that someone pasted a new article to html form <br><br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$diff </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">xdiff_string_diff</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$old_article</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$new_article</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">1</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>if (</span><span style="color: #9876AA">is_string</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$diff</span><span style="color: #007700">)) {<br>    echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Differences between two articles:\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>    echo </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$diff</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>}<br><br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 notes" id="refsect1-function.xdiff-string-diff-notes">  <h3 class="title">注释</h3>  <blockquote class="note" style="border:1px gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">注意</strong>:    </p><p class="para">    This function doesn't work well with binary strings. To make diff of binary    strings use <span class="function">{@link xdiff_string_bdiff()}</span>/<span class="function">{@link xdiff_string_rabdiff()}</span>.   </p>  </blockquote> </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.xdiff-string-diff-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link xdiff_string_patch()} - Patch a string with an unified diff</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
